00:06:57.366 --> 00:07:00.696 A:middle
And, thirdly, Check out with

00:07:00.696 --> 00:07:01.136 A:middle
Apple Pay.

00:07:02.176 --> 00:07:03.406 A:middle
This is best used if you have

00:07:03.406 --> 00:07:05.136 A:middle
multiple references to checkout

00:07:05.556 --> 00:07:06.446 A:middle
on the same page.

00:07:07.316 --> 00:07:08.736 A:middle
Now, this really makes it clear

00:07:08.736 --> 00:07:10.676 A:middle
to the user exactly which

00:07:10.676 --> 00:07:13.276 A:middle
checkout performs Apple Pay.

00:07:14.256 --> 00:07:15.806 A:middle
That's not all the changes to

00:07:15.806 --> 00:07:16.176 A:middle
the button.

00:07:17.216 --> 00:07:18.736 A:middle
You know that we love rounded

00:07:18.736 --> 00:07:20.016 A:middle
corners and continuous curves,

00:07:20.526 --> 00:07:21.496 A:middle
but we understand that not

00:07:21.496 --> 00:07:22.496 A:middle
everybody shares exactly the

00:07:22.496 --> 00:07:24.316 A:middle
same feelings, and so this year,

00:07:25.006 --> 00:07:26.026 A:middle
we're allowing you to control

00:07:26.026 --> 00:07:28.956 A:middle
the corner edits of the button.

00:07:29.126 --> 00:07:30.506 A:middle
You can configure this however

00:07:30.506 --> 00:07:32.066 A:middle
you see fit to match existing

00:07:32.066 --> 00:07:33.926 A:middle
styles of your apps or websites.

00:07:35.596 --> 00:07:37.166 A:middle
If you want square corners,

00:07:37.246 --> 00:07:38.556 A:middle
simply set the button radius to

00:07:38.556 --> 00:07:38.876 A:middle
0.

00:07:39.436 --> 00:07:42.126 A:middle
And, if you set no value, our

00:07:42.126 --> 00:07:43.266 A:middle
existing corner radius will be

00:07:43.266 --> 00:07:43.626 A:middle
used.

00:07:44.826 --> 00:07:46.306 A:middle
Now, similarly, on older

00:07:46.306 --> 00:07:47.436 A:middle
versions, the button will

00:07:47.436 --> 00:07:48.756 A:middle
fallback to using the current

00:07:48.756 --> 00:07:50.416 A:middle
rounded corner radius, ignoring

00:07:50.416 --> 00:07:51.526 A:middle
any value that you've set.

00:07:54.296 --> 00:07:55.616 A:middle
The new types and corner radius

00:07:55.616 --> 00:07:56.746 A:middle
are available in iOS 12 today.

00:07:56.836 --> 00:07:58.156 A:middle
And, they're coming to WebKit in

00:07:58.156 --> 00:07:58.896 A:middle
a future release.

